plot: A woman falls in love with a man nicknamed 'The Bohemian'. Her family and friends warn her that he is not the marrying kind. When he does eventually leave her, she makes up her mind to wait for the unlikely day when he will return.
title: Seulpeumeun gangmulcheoreom
